name: LunchPicker
0: ”Alexa, ask lunch picker to give me a suggestion”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lunch picker
des: When it comes time for a meal, do you ever have a hard time figuring out what to make or pickup? Well, this app is supposed to aid you in the everyday struggle of indecisiveness -- aiding you in your drought of hunger. No longer will you be spending excessive amounts of time just trying to figure out what to eat, now you can simply ask this app what you should have. From there, you can stop worrying about what to eat, and just get it or make it yourself.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
